Short : HD-Installer for Dominator V1.1
Type : game/patch
Author :  Bored Seal & JOTD

This patch applies to "Dominator" by System 3 (c) 1989 - 1 disk.
Slave requires WHDLOAD V17+.
Game requires 0.5 MB Chip Mem (+ 0.4 other memory for preload option)

FEATURES:
- Full load from HD
- RNC disk protection removed
- Access faults fixed
- CPU dependant loops fixed
- Highscores will be saved
- Trainer option added (set CUSTOM1=1 tooltype for unlimited lives)
- NI/ROM icon (created by JHZ)
- Quit option (press LMB in game)

HISTORY:
V0.9 (08-Dec-2000) - first public release (beta)
V1.0 (08-Feb-2001) - final release - access faults fixed, proper quit option
                   - trainer option, highscore support added
                   - snoop mode bug fixed
V2.0 (15-Jul-2017) - adapted to WHDLoad 17
                   - added quitkey for 68000 & fixed keyboard handler (issue #0003680)
				   
Thanks to Carlo Pirri for diskimage.

         Bug report form, full WHDLoad package and other installs:
                          http://www.whdload.de
